00:05:42.258 --> 00:05:44.101
Don't be in a rush.

00:05:44.719 --> 00:05:48.222
I'm Yi Fu's uncle, after all.

00:05:48.222 --> 00:05:49.349
Here's the thing.

00:05:49.349 --> 00:05:51.601
If there's anything between you and Yi Fu,

00:05:51.601 --> 00:05:53.186
you can share it with me.

00:05:53.186 --> 00:05:55.480
I have a lot of tips for you.

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:56.773
Listen to me.

00:05:56.773 --> 00:05:59.400
Often, when it comes to relationships...

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:02.452
