00:21:44.970 --> 00:21:46.604
I know.

00:21:47.389 --> 00:21:48.765
Where's Dr. Gu?

00:21:48.765 --> 00:21:50.017
He's not here.

00:21:50.017 --> 00:21:51.776
Where is he?

00:21:54.438 --> 00:21:56.030
New Zealand.

00:21:57.941 --> 00:22:01.077
We're moving to New Zealand for good.

00:22:09.119 --> 00:22:12.380
There's no need to call.
He won't answer your calls.

00:22:13.040 --> 00:22:15.292
He won't see you again.

00:22:15.292 --> 00:22:17.385
Just give up.

00:22:18.545 --> 00:22:22.014
Sorry, the number you dialed is unavailable.

00:22:41.568 --> 00:22:42.652
Where is he?

00:22:42.652 --> 00:22:44.154
Sorry, the number you dialed...

00:22:44.154 --> 00:22:46.156
- His phone is with me.
- ...is unavailable.

00:22:46.156 --> 00:22:48.166
Please try again later.

00:22:52.746 --> 00:22:54.338
Don't glare at me.

00:22:55.207 --> 00:22:56.924
Show yourself out.

00:23:46.342 --> 00:23:48.385
I went to your house. I wanted to tell you...

00:23:48.385 --> 00:23:51.229
Are you going to New Zealand with Fan Yue Jiao?

00:24:02.607 --> 00:24:05.284
She's threatening me with money.

00:24:07.946 --> 00:24:09.747
I'll go with her first.

00:24:10.824 --> 00:24:12.959
I'll try to get the money back.

00:24:17.706 --> 00:24:20.125
Don't go.

00:24:20.125 --> 00:24:22.419
If you go, you won't come back.

00:24:22.419 --> 00:24:24.553
It's such a mess now.

00:24:25.964 --> 00:24:28.467
There's nothing I can do.

00:24:28.467 --> 00:24:31.535
I'll find a way to send you
the money I owe you.

00:24:57.204 --> 00:25:00.798
I've never been a choice to you, have I?

00:25:02.959 --> 00:25:05.636
This is the best decision for everyone.

00:25:07.047 --> 00:25:10.808
Please take good care of yourself.

00:25:12.677 --> 00:25:16.181
Do you love Fan Yue Jiao more than you love me?

00:25:16.181 --> 00:25:17.584
Is that it?

00:25:22.437 --> 00:25:24.030
I'm sorry.

00:25:26.274 --> 00:25:28.743
Is that your answer?

00:25:29.444 --> 00:25:31.412
Gu Hou Ze!

00:26:13.947 --> 00:26:16.116
Why are you out in the rain?

00:26:16.116 --> 00:26:18.334
Come in.

00:26:20.287 --> 00:26:21.871
Why are you looking for me?

00:26:21.871 --> 00:26:23.582
I have something important to tell you.

00:26:23.582 --> 00:26:25.841
Sit down first.

00:26:30.880 --> 00:26:33.008
Xiao Qi.

00:26:33.008 --> 00:26:35.309
You're pregnant.

00:26:36.970 --> 00:26:39.472
It was confirmed during the last check-up.

00:26:39.472 --> 00:26:43.018
I'm just as shocked as you.

00:26:43.018 --> 00:26:46.438
I thought we'd need
medical technology to have a child.

00:26:46.438 --> 00:26:49.031
But it really happened.

00:26:50.692 --> 00:26:53.317
Wait a minute.

00:27:06.124 --> 00:27:10.094
Xiao Qi, will you marry me?

00:27:10.712 --> 00:27:13.840
You can plan the wedding as you please.

00:27:13.840 --> 00:27:17.010
And I want to give you a grand wedding gift.

00:27:17.010 --> 00:27:19.721
Just tell me what you want.

00:27:19.721 --> 00:27:21.507
I'll definitely agree.

00:27:40.950 --> 00:27:42.494
Hello?

00:27:42.494 --> 00:27:44.753
When are you leaving?

00:27:47.916 --> 00:27:49.550
This afternoon.

00:27:50.460 --> 00:27:52.720
I want to meet you now.

00:28:04.974 --> 00:28:07.560
Your call will be forwarded to voicemail.

00:28:07.560 --> 00:28:10.029
You will be charged after the beep.

00:28:42.220 --> 00:28:44.188
Yue Jiao.

00:28:47.392 --> 00:28:49.046
Yue Jiao.

00:29:08.204 --> 00:29:10.673
Why did you let me in here?

00:29:14.169 --> 00:29:16.387
Can you do me a favor?

00:29:37.859 --> 00:29:40.661
Can you change into this?

00:29:42.822 --> 00:29:45.040
These are Shu Juan's clothes.

00:29:45.784 --> 00:29:49.336
Today is the second anniversary
of her and Xiao An's passing.

00:29:50.747 --> 00:29:53.291
I can't believe a car accident

00:29:53.291 --> 00:29:56.135
took them both away from me.

00:30:02.008 --> 00:30:03.507
Sure.

00:30:20.902 --> 00:30:23.412
When Shu Juan was around,

00:30:24.280 --> 00:30:27.492
we used to go dancing a lot.

00:30:27.492 --> 00:30:29.418
Those days...

00:30:30.453 --> 00:30:32.254
were truly wonderful.

00:31:06.823 --> 00:31:08.957
You didn't bring an umbrella again, did you?

00:31:09.576 --> 00:31:11.168
I'll give you a ride.

00:31:15.623 --> 00:31:18.133
You can take my car. I'll give you a ride.

00:31:22.755 --> 00:31:25.174
Haven't we decided to be friends?

00:31:25.174 --> 00:31:28.261
Please don't keep doing things
that'll cause misunderstandings.

00:31:28.261 --> 00:31:29.804
What do you mean by that?

00:31:29.804 --> 00:31:30.984
But it's raining heavily.

00:31:30.984 --> 00:31:32.473
Take my car. I'll give you a ride.

00:31:32.473 --> 00:31:34.358
Don't overthink it.

00:32:10.887 --> 00:32:12.764
Get in the car. You're all wet.

00:32:12.764 --> 00:32:14.349
I want to take the bus.

00:32:14.349 --> 00:32:16.184
Why take the bus when I can drive you?

00:32:16.184 --> 00:32:17.769
I love taking the bus.

00:32:17.769 --> 00:32:19.695
Your car is uncomfortable.

00:32:23.691 --> 00:32:25.044
Fuck.

00:32:31.324 --> 00:32:32.909
Can you stop being so difficult?

00:32:32.909 --> 00:32:35.169
I'm not as casual as you.

00:32:39.207 --> 00:32:40.458
I may have only dated for a short time,

00:32:40.458 --> 00:32:42.543
but I've never cheated.

00:32:42.543 --> 00:32:43.920
Isn't that great?

00:32:43.920 --> 00:32:45.588
You only date for three months.

00:32:45.588 --> 00:32:47.306
It's just a fling.

00:32:56.265 --> 00:32:58.317
How long do you want it to last?

00:33:01.646 --> 00:33:03.439
Sir.

00:33:03.439 --> 00:33:06.776
It's normal for relationships
to have ups and downs.

00:33:06.776 --> 00:33:09.988
I'm not someone who needs it to last forever.

00:33:09.988 --> 00:33:12.615
Who sets a time limit like that?

00:33:12.615 --> 00:33:14.492
Then don't set one.

00:33:14.492 --> 00:33:16.744
Let's just try to be together.

00:33:16.744 --> 00:33:18.918
We'll see how long it lasts.

00:33:25.545 --> 00:33:26.838
Let's date.

00:33:26.838 --> 00:33:28.244
What do you think?

00:33:36.556 --> 00:33:39.267
How can you say that so casually?

00:33:39.267 --> 00:33:41.644
Who knows if you're serious or not?

00:33:41.644 --> 00:33:43.062
I'm not made of time.

00:33:43.062 --> 00:33:46.156
Why would I put in so much effort
to lie to you?

00:33:49.944 --> 00:33:53.489
So, you're willing to bend
your principles for me?

00:33:53.489 --> 00:33:56.084
You seemed really reluctant before.

00:33:57.243 --> 00:34:00.580
I was figuring out what I should do.

00:34:00.580 --> 00:34:03.791
I thought I'd talk to you
when I'd made up my mind.

00:34:03.791 --> 00:34:06.127
Besides, it was so awkward between us.

00:34:06.127 --> 00:34:07.761
How could I speak my mind?

00:34:09.589 --> 00:34:11.090
You didn't say anything.

00:34:11.090 --> 00:34:13.885
Of course I'd think you were avoiding me.

00:34:13.885 --> 00:34:16.863
I rushed back because
I didn't want you to think that way.

00:34:19.932 --> 00:34:22.602
I met some farmers when I was
on a business trip in the south.

00:34:22.602 --> 00:34:25.480
They were growing the flowers they bred.

00:34:25.480 --> 00:34:28.858
The flowers wither in three months.

00:34:28.858 --> 00:34:30.693
The farmers also said,

00:34:30.693 --> 00:34:34.489
"It's better to keep a wonderful past."

00:34:34.489 --> 00:34:35.782
When I heard them say that,

00:34:35.782 --> 00:34:38.743
I suddenly felt sad.

00:34:38.743 --> 00:34:40.747
That was when I thought of you.

00:34:46.042 --> 00:34:49.261
I don't think I want to
end it in three months with you.

00:34:53.800 --> 00:34:56.803
It just so happens that it's also three months?

00:34:56.803 --> 00:34:58.562
You're bluffing, right?

00:35:02.350 --> 00:35:06.104
Yes, I'm bluffing.

00:35:06.104 --> 00:35:08.530
The gist is...

00:35:10.775 --> 00:35:12.743
I miss you.

00:35:19.575 --> 00:35:21.710
You blabbered on and on...

00:35:22.912 --> 00:35:25.172
But the summary was way more romantic.

00:35:41.239 --> 00:35:43.019
So, do you agree?

00:35:48.396 --> 00:35:50.606
When you promised it'll last
more than three months...

00:35:50.606 --> 00:35:52.975
you didn't mean just four months, right?

00:35:57.113 --> 00:35:59.282
When you turn 40,

00:35:59.282 --> 00:36:01.826
I'll still celebrate your birthday with you.

00:36:01.826 --> 00:36:05.246
Happy birthday to you.

00:36:05.246 --> 00:36:06.622
What?

00:36:06.622 --> 00:36:07.999
Louder, I can't hear you.

00:36:07.999 --> 00:36:11.085
Happy birthday to you.

00:36:11.085 --> 00:36:13.387
Happy birthday!

00:36:14.422 --> 00:36:16.090
When you turn 50,

00:36:16.090 --> 00:36:17.842
I'll still celebrate your birthday with you.

00:36:17.842 --> 00:36:20.560
Happy birthday!

00:36:21.971 --> 00:36:23.944
I've blown out the candles.

00:36:25.141 --> 00:36:26.984
Can I make a wish now?

00:36:29.478 --> 00:36:31.488
What do you want to wish for?

00:36:38.613 --> 00:36:40.580
Can I stick my tongue in?

00:37:25.034 --> 00:37:27.335
Xiao Qi, you're so pretty today.

00:37:28.454 --> 00:37:30.080
Thank you.

00:37:33.960 --> 00:37:36.344
But you'll look prettier if you smile.

00:37:38.005 --> 00:37:40.012
I'll smile later.

00:38:16.088 --> 00:38:18.629
What is it that needs to be said in person?

00:39:14.602 --> 00:39:17.094
If the debts can be paid off,

00:39:19.148 --> 00:39:21.992
will you stay and turn your life
upside-down with me?

00:39:44.757 --> 00:39:46.558
I'm pregnant.

00:39:50.012 --> 00:39:51.855
It's your child.

00:40:17.039 --> 00:40:19.375
Xiao Qi, we...

00:40:46.402 --> 00:40:48.049
Let's go.

00:41:11.010 --> 00:41:13.645
This is the best solution
I've come up with so far.

00:41:14.430 --> 00:41:17.057
Is this another form of revenge?

00:41:17.057 --> 00:41:19.143
After I marry him,
he'll give me a sum of money.

00:41:19.143 --> 00:41:20.853
It can temporarily pay off your debts.

00:41:20.853 --> 00:41:23.905
You won't have to leave. You can stay.

00:41:24.735 --> 00:41:26.328
Stay?

00:41:27.276 --> 00:41:30.070
The marriage is just a show.

00:41:30.070 --> 00:41:33.257
Once your debts are paid off,
I'll take our child and leave him.

00:41:37.495 --> 00:41:39.838
Your idea is too naive.

00:41:42.082 --> 00:41:44.050
It's not an idea.

00:41:45.044 --> 00:41:47.132
It's what I've decided.

00:41:52.843 --> 00:41:55.312
Do you like it when I'm so naive?

00:42:03.646 --> 00:42:07.216
I've never been a choice to you, have I?

00:42:08.567 --> 00:42:11.499
This is the best decision for everyone.

00:43:27.021 --> 00:43:30.024
Fine, Old Wu can give a speech.

00:43:30.024 --> 00:43:34.111
But even Chairman Fu
and Chairman Kang wanted air time.

00:43:34.111 --> 00:43:36.204
They never have anything interesting to say.

00:43:44.204 --> 00:43:48.125
What's wrong? Are you tired?

00:43:48.125 --> 00:43:50.711
Of course, I've been smiling all day.

00:43:50.711 --> 00:43:52.921
It's only one day of exhaustion.

00:43:52.921 --> 00:43:53.964
From now on,

00:43:53.964 --> 00:43:57.384
you can just relax and be the chairman's wife.

00:43:57.384 --> 00:44:01.187
And have a healthy baby.

00:44:03.057 --> 00:44:05.559
By the way, I've appointed a driver for you.

00:44:05.559 --> 00:44:08.437
You're pregnant now. Don't drive.

00:44:08.437 --> 00:44:11.357
But my job requires me to travel.
That'll be inconvenient.

00:44:11.357 --> 00:44:13.859
Your status is different now.

00:44:13.859 --> 00:44:16.737
Driving that small car around?

00:44:16.737 --> 00:44:20.040
What would others say about me?

00:44:27.915 --> 00:44:30.209
The will and the transfer of trust

00:44:30.209 --> 00:44:32.503
has been amended as per your instructions.

00:44:32.503 --> 00:44:34.554
Please take a look.

00:44:35.714 --> 00:44:39.350
If there are no issues, please sign it.

00:44:43.976 --> 00:44:52.918
[Zhan Qian Ren]

00:44:55.567 --> 00:44:58.195
Thank you, Attorney Ren.

00:44:58.195 --> 00:44:59.528
It's my pleasure.

00:45:10.624 --> 00:45:11.854
Are you going out?

00:45:11.854 --> 00:45:13.836
To a consultation.

00:45:13.836 --> 00:45:15.655
Haven't you been sleeping better lately?

00:45:15.655 --> 00:45:16.964
You still have sessions?

00:45:16.964 --> 00:45:19.842
I'll feel better if I talk to the doctor.

00:45:19.842 --> 00:45:21.802
I'm glad it helps.

00:45:21.802 --> 00:45:24.805
Your mood is most important now.

00:45:24.805 --> 00:45:26.473
Ask the driver to take you.

00:45:26.473 --> 00:45:28.650
- I'll get going then.
- Okay.

00:45:59.506 --> 00:46:01.975
Qian Ren got me a driver.

00:46:05.095 --> 00:46:08.188
I think he wants to
keep an eye on us. Be careful.

00:46:13.270 --> 00:46:16.364
I don't know how long this will last.

00:46:18.275 --> 00:46:20.076
Yeah.

00:46:25.115 --> 00:46:26.916
The baby kicked me.

00:46:28.952 --> 00:46:30.454
That's too soon.

00:46:30.454 --> 00:46:31.933
The baby's really kicking me.

00:46:31.933 --> 00:46:33.582
Feel it if you don't believe me.

00:46:33.582 --> 00:46:35.008
Here.

00:46:35.918 --> 00:46:37.377
Do you feel it?

00:46:37.377 --> 00:46:40.047
Here. Do you feel it?

00:46:40.047 --> 00:46:42.089
You must've eaten too much ice cream.

00:46:42.089 --> 00:46:43.759
Your stomach is bloated.

00:46:43.759 --> 00:46:45.928
- It's rumbling.
- The baby really kicked me.

00:46:45.928 --> 00:46:47.346
Why don't you believe me?

00:46:47.346 --> 00:46:49.731
Yes, I feel it.

00:47:16.041 --> 00:47:17.626
Why are you here?

00:47:17.626 --> 00:47:19.927
Mr. Zhan asked me to...

00:47:21.505 --> 00:47:22.798
You forgot your phone.

00:47:22.798 --> 00:47:24.474
Thank you.

00:47:26.385 --> 00:47:29.805
Hello, Dr. Gu. I'm a fan of yours.

00:47:29.805 --> 00:47:31.496
I've read all your books.

00:47:31.496 --> 00:47:33.225
They encouraged me greatly.

00:47:33.225 --> 00:47:34.476
Thank you.

00:47:34.476 --> 00:47:36.728
Make an appointment with the receptionist
for our next session.

00:47:36.728 --> 00:47:38.138
Okay.

00:47:43.777 --> 00:47:45.745
Why are you here?

00:47:46.822 --> 00:47:48.740
Mr. Zhan said to change the family registry.

00:47:48.740 --> 00:47:51.034
We need your ID and seal.

00:47:51.034 --> 00:47:52.369
I asked the driver and he said you were here.

00:47:52.369 --> 00:47:53.495
- That's why I'm here.
- Ask me directly next time.

00:47:53.495 --> 00:47:55.303
Don't ask the driver.

00:49:36.848 --> 00:49:38.850
Who let you take Shu Juan's stuff?

00:49:38.850 --> 00:49:42.570
I...

00:49:45.816 --> 00:49:47.784
Zhan Qian Ren!